Problem Statement : Calculate Trip Cost
==================

Display Hotel name, total amount for first 3 hotels:

1. For 4 people in any location for 5 days of stay from tomorrow's date.
2. Sort the list with highest User rating.
3. Show hotels with free Wifi, free breakfast and amenities with laundry and swimming pool.

Detailed Description: 
====================

Calculate Trip Cost

Step-1
=======
Display Hotel name, total amount for first 3 hotels for 4 people in any location for 5 days of stay 
from tomorrow's date.

Step-2
=======
Should have sorted the list of hotels with highest User rating. 

Step-3
=======
Show hotels with free Wifi, free breakfast and amenities with laundry and swimming pool.

Step-4
=======
Pick any one cruise line 
      a. Retrieve all the Inclusion points and Display the same
      
Step-5
=======
Go to gift voucher and scroll to corporate queries and fill it with invalid email and phone number.
	  a. capture error message and display the same.

(Suggested Site: www.yatra.com however  you are free to choose any other legitimate  site)


Key Automation Scope:
====================

1.)Handling different browser windows, search option
2.)Validation of date controls
3.)Capture warning message
4.)Extract list items & store in collections
5.)Navigating back to home page
6.)Scrolling down in web page

Note: Take all necessary screenshots for all the testcases and print all the data in the console.

Frame Works Used:
=================
1)Testng
2)Maven
3)Cucumber

